{
  "stem": "6845.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my mother made it very, very clear that if I just look up, that is a fact of life-- that the stomach has to be satisfied and con-- you know, treated well.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "OK, Mother, so I learned that one real fast.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then when I was sitting at the table, I had to sit very-- not just me, but my two brothers too-- we had to behave and sit just so, because if no, we might be sent away from the table.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I found out a wonderful gimmick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I would take out one of the soft breads from the table, put it in my lap.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I had a napkin there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I sat beautifully straight, looking up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And meantime, with my two hands, I was creating little animals, birds mainly, or cows, and flowers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And each one was around, like, one inch long.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I would put them on the toothpick, right next to my place setting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And whoever sat next to me had a chance to make a comment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And usually, they was very much admired and appreciated, and I felt good.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so then, I would look at my mother and say, could I go, please, to the kitchen and bake a-- the lady next to me-- I don't know who they were, but probably they were friends of the family or relatives-- that they like it?",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my mother, all right, child.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You can go to the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I would go to the oven, bake it for five minutes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now I brought it back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was dry, and it was-- I don't have to worry that it is brittle.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It will burn, right, [? and it will ?] be destroyed.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
